videoDetails.title: The 30-Second Video
videoDetails.shortDescription:
Watch my new videos at https://www.youtube.com/user/NoSmallPartsShow

I heard somewhere that nowadays, people won't pay attention to most videos that are longer than 30 seconds.

This one's for you, Sammy Jenkis.

I used Garageband and recorded this Bobby McFerrin style. With the exception of the beat in the background, I did all the vocals.

title.simpleText: The 30-Second Video

description.simpleText:
Watch my new videos at https://www.youtube.com/user/NoSmallPartsShow

I heard somewhere that nowadays, people won't pay attention to most videos that are longer than 30 seconds.

This one's for you, Sammy Jenkis.

I used Garageband and recorded this Bobby McFerrin style. With the exception of the beat in the background, I did all the vocals.
